  "title": "Legal Executive",
  "description": "<p>1.                LVM  Law Chambers LLC is a boutique legal firm which specialises in dispute resolution. We are led by an eminent Senior Counsel, Lok Vi Ming S.C. Our team is young, dynamic, and collegiate.<br /></p><p>2.              We are looking for a Legal Executive to join our growing team. As a Legal Executive, you will be working with all our practice groups, to support our lawyers in day-to-day legal work. The role involves handling legal\n  documentation, case management, and liaising with clients and external parties.<br /></p><p>3.                Applicants should have:</p><p>(a)      A law degree from a local law school or a foreign law school;</p><p>(b)     Strong analytical, communication, and writing skills; and</p><p>(c)      “a passion for litigation and to work in a dynamic team.”<br /></p><p>4.                If you are interested in applying, please send in your cover letter and detailed\n  resume to us at legalcareer@lvmlawchambers.com. Only shortlisted candidates\n  will be notified.</p>",
